text: Ray Sorensen (May 12, 1922 - December 17, 1974) was an American gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:1974 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:People from Warren, Pennsylvania
